 />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6588a987af7caec8ce9f7e9043a673575e62fb","tid":317081,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:18:30.000Z","msg":"study plan:<br />\n<br />\nyear 1 sem A<br />\n-Introduction to Computer Studies /<br />\nIntroduction to Computer Programming -<br />\nGE (1)<br />\n<br />\n-Calculus and Basic Linear Algebra I /<br />\nEnhanced Calculus and Linear Algebra I -<br />\nGE (2)<br />\n<br />\n-General Physics I /<br />\nChemistry (pre-reg.) /<br />\nDiscovery in Biology (pre-reg.)<br />\n<br />\n-University English &ndash; GE (3)<br />\n<br />\n-Fundamentals of Internet Applications<br />\nDevelopmen<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsem B<br />\n-English for Engineering &ndash; GE (4) <br />\n<br />\n-Calculus and Basic Linear Algebra II /<br />\nEnhanced Calculus and Linear Algebra II -<br />\nGE(5)<br />\n<br />\n-General Physics I (pre-reg.) /<br />\nChemistry /<br />\nDiscovery in Biology (pre-reg.) <br />\n<br />\n-Probability in Action: From the Unfinished<br />\nGame to the Modern World<br />\n<br />\n-Computer Programming"},{"pid":"eae7429eada9b94809df46ac898267216acc7e4f","tid":317081,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"我文商科底去讀會唔會好辛苦？身體有無同學都係咁"},{"pid":"ba7dc96c40ec9046968efc32c15ea111c27e008a","tid":317081,"uid":10140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:23:04.000Z","msg":"今次預計收幾分？"},{"pid":"9944d7818a1e431dd44947c853b38f48c3e031b5","tid":317081,"uid":46047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T08:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我文商科底去讀會唔會好辛苦？身體有無同學都係咁</blockquote><br />\n首先year 1已經要讀phy chem bio其中兩科<br />\n同埋year 1有2科數要你讀<br />\n而個兩科數 你有m1/m2底讀會好好多<br />\n如果你冇底會追得有啲辛苦<br />\n同埋就算係programming既科 你冇底既話都要花唔少時間去溫<br />\n所以希望你考慮清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c56cad01fe69286c4f4b90